            "description": "This project was part of our graduation period of our study, Environmental Science, at the University of Applied Sciences HAS Den Bosch in The Netherlands. For a period of almost five months we worked as Junior Advisors for HAS KennisTransfer, a consultancy company in \u2018s-Hertogenbosch in The Netherlands. During this period we did a project for S.E.S.A. SpA in Este (PD), Italy. We were supervised by project manager Rene Schoorl, who has extensive knowledge and experience in the field of wastewater treatment.\n\n- Analysis at a wastewater treatment plant in Italy and experiments in the laboratory.\n- Calculations on wastewater treatment plant loads and nitrogen removal processes.\n- Extensive literature investigation on different nitrogen removal processes.",
